wikipedia_page.main: Alan Henry Brooke, 3rd Viscount Brookeborough,  (born 30 June 1952), is a Northern Irish peer and landowner. He is one of the 92 hereditary peers who remain in the House of Lords; he sits as a crossbencher. He is the current Lord Lieutenant of Fermanagh.
